name: HUITZIL I
description:
Hummingbirds are carriers of good toughts.  In aztec cosmogony they represent the spirit of the warrior.  

Temple of Masks is a collaborative project created for Virtual Burning Man 2021. Part of a series of videoart and animated NFT´s by Cryptofangs.
